snippet.title: Attack On Reality Update 1 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out Now

Attack on Reality is a recreation of the popular anime/manga Attack on Titan, in Virtual Reality, that aims to be as faithful as possible to the source material.

Take control of a scout as you fly through the air with Omni-Directional Mobility Gear.

Join the discord at https://discord.gg/wACkurf
Follow us on GameJolt at https://gamejolt.com/games/AoR/342878
Itch.io: https://yurogamedev.itch.io/aor
Sidequest: https://sidequestvr.com/app/2407/attack-on-reality

Attack on Reality is created by Yu Ro

Trailer created/edited by Rtasva: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuRb4xybe2gVyxMCfSaun7w

Additional Help
-Yu Ro (Direction/Footage)
-Laserpants (Footage)
-Corrupt (Footage)
-Azazeal (Footage)
-Travzzz (Digital Art)

Attack on Titan is created by Hajime Isayama and is a registered trademark of Kodansha Ltd.

Attack on Titan's original soundtrack is composed by Hiroyuki Sawano and copyrighted by Pony Canyon Inc
